title: Ryan Decenzo - Create Your Vision - The Ledge
description:
Ryan Decenzo and the Arnette skate team wanted to give something back to the skateboarding community, so they created a buttery new ledge at a legendary Southern California spot. Skating by Chris Joslin, Scott Decenzo, Ryan Decenzo, Pat Duffy, and Mark Appleyard.

Ryan Decenzo wears the Dropout, get yours at http://www.arnette.com
